    <!-- SECTION 1 — HERO SECTION -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-grid">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <span class="hero-author">A Contemporary Romance Novel</span>
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Tested Hearts<span>2: Silent Vows</span></h1>
                    <p class="hero-tagline">“He would choose silence until words mattered.”</p>
                    <p class="hero-hook">
                        In the vibrant corridors of Shri Varma Engineering College, Rohit Sharma carries a reputation for falling too fast. But when he encounters Saanvi, a quiet, self-contained soul guarded by ancient family walls, the noise of quick infatuation dissolves into an unspoken language of glances, structural patience, and lifelong promises kept across a silent decade.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-book-area">
