    <!-- SECTION 2 — STORY SECTION -->
    <section id="story" class="story-section section-offset">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="section-label">The Synopsis</span>
            <h2 class="section-heading">An Anatomy of Patience</h2>
            <div class="story-layout">
                <div class="story-text">
                    <div class="story-featured-quote">
                        “Everyone else in college saw a guy hovering in the periphery of a girl he liked. Only the three of them knew it was a language distances kept.”
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Rohit Sharma has a history of wearing his heart on his sleeve, proposing to ten different girls through his third year at Shri Varma Engineering College. He didn't chase flashy beauty; he fell for simple, unassuming kindness. Yet, his impulsiveness brought gossip and polite rejections, shaping him into a campus caricature.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Everything changes when destiny enters his own living room in the form of Saanvi, his college sister Meera's best friend. Saanvi is unlike anyone Rohit has known. She is deeply private, guarded by strict traditional roots, and hyper-aware of the deep caste divisions between them. Rather than rushing blindly forward, Rohit makes a radical choice: he elects to speak through action, establishing a wordless lexicon of small, home-shaped gestures.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        When traditional pressures force Saanvi into an arranged marriage with another man, Rohit refuses to let bitterness erode his heart. He chooses to stand still, trusting the gravity of a silent vow made on a rainy terrace, waiting through eight long, solitary years until destiny circles back to a quiet classroom doorway.
                    </p>
                    <div class="themes-wrapper">
                        <h4 class="themes-title">Core Themes Explored</h4>
                        <div class="theme-tags">
                            <span class="theme-tag">Unspoken Devotion</span>
                            <span class="theme-tag">Caste & Traditional Barriers</span>
                            <span class="theme-tag">The Architecture of Silence</span>
                            <span class="theme-tag">Second-Chance Fate</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-num">21</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Chapters</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-num">2</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Perspectives</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-num">8+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Years Timespan</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <span class="stat-num">OC/BC</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Social Dynamic</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
